<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the QuickStart on the "Create a Model and Database Table" page in the app.ini code sample the following line incorrectly references the SQLite database file:</p>

<p>database.params.dbname = APPLICATION_PATH "/../data/db/guestbook.db"</p>

<p>I believe it should be:</p>

<p>database.params.dbname = APPLICATION_PATH "/data/db/guestbook.db"</p>

<p>Also, the paragraph following the bootstrap.php code sample should also be modified if the database is actually located in the /application/data/db/ directory and not the application/data/ directory as the page states.</p>

